  "title": "Freight Sales Executive #74828",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Freight Forwarding</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Freight Sales Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tampines</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 8.30am – 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary + Commission + Transport Allowance + Mobile Allowance</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Achieve sales revenue and profit goals.</li><li>Manage client accounts and learn about the market to find new sales leads.</li><li>Negotiate contracts and close sales deals.</li><li>Handle customer feedback and complaints, providing after-sales support.</li><li>Serve as the main contact for customers, working closely with departments to address their needs.</li><li>Follow up with existing and in-house clients to ensure quality service.</li><li>Respond to in-house customer inquiries and requirements as needed.</li><li>Submit daily reports, sales reports, and sales plans.</li><li>Prepare quotations and administrative reports.</li><li>Participate in all company activities and initiatives.</li><li>Perform other tasks assigned by management.</li><li>Complete additional administrative duties as required by the Manager.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 2 years of sales experience in the shipping or freight forwarding industry.</li><li>Ability to identify and secure new accounts.</li><li>Capable of working independently in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Customer-focused, goal-oriented, motivated, responsible, detail-oriented, and a strong negotiator.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#74828 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
